{"tid":1511643,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［文宣] 1 分鐘喚醒海外香港發生咩事，點解關佢地事","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:14:22.000Z","uid":157860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3964ba085b20bcd908e7aeef0f8dbd4c6897aa","tid":1511643,"uid":157860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"香港最入屋係咩？ 係電視<br />\n海外都係，用全球最受歡迎嘅電視劇比喻香港發生咩事，點解要同香港同一陣線 ! <br />\n睇過嘅，立即知道咩事。當然未睇過就無辦法<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅係 Game Of Thrones， 香港人就好似 Night Watch 咁，負責守衛北邊做哨兵，做前線頂住不死人。<br />\n<br />\nNight Watch 一直無人留意，俾人流放，響城牆上自生自滅<br />\n中土七國 （G7 ? ) 不斷內戰，就好似而家左派右派為啲環保、LGBT 不斷起紛爭<br />\n但係 Winter is coming，一班會侵蝕世界嘅力量一直想翻牆出尼，此仗一敗，黑暗即將籠罩世界<br />\n劇入面 Night Watch 寡不敵眾，但最後成功號召中土國家一齊抵抗<br />\n劇入面好多符號令人充滿聯想，城牆，飛龍...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozD481k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozD481k.jpg&h=6b658b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLK76N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLK76N1.jpg&h=03f2df08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f971f625fa8c3a04a843827ac654f17aef37e1f4","tid":1511643,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=3b4ee699\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=524eb335\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳